Backend for MovieWatchList app built with Node.js, Express, MongoDB, and JWT authentication.

## Features
- User authentication (JWT)
- Add / remove movies
- Mark movies as watched
- User-specific watchlists

## Tech Stack
- Node.js
- Express
- MongoDB Atlas
- JWT Authentication

## Setup
1. Clone repo
2. Install dependencies
   npm install
3. Create .env file
   MONGO_URI=your_mongo_url
   JWT_SECRET=your_secret
4. Run server
   npm start
